0:02:27.900,0:02:31.000
The Household Department now
sends us only the best of everything.

0:02:31.100,0:02:33.840
Everyone knows how much His Majesty likes you, My Lady.

0:02:33.840,0:02:37.140
He also instructed Mr Wen to make tonics for you every day.

0:02:37.200,0:02:39.600
You'd think it as a treat.
The medicine is all bitterness.

0:02:42.480,0:02:45.700
Speaking of bitterness,

0:02:45.700,0:02:49.720
Yu has been cursing you bitterly since her demotion.

0:02:49.720,0:02:51.580
Let her be.

0:02:51.580,0:02:55.460
I have a clear conscience.
Her curses won't be fulfilled.

0:02:55.460,0:02:58.640
But they are too unpleasant to hear.

0:02:58.640,0:03:02.100
What about I report it to the Empress?
She'll hold Yu responsible.

0:03:02.100,0:03:06.060
That's more trouble than it's worth.
"Forgive a mistake when you can."

0:03:06.060,0:03:09.900
She'll be fine after a while.

0:03:10.000,0:03:12.960
That is very kind of you, My Lady.

0:03:14.000,0:03:16.200
My Lady, the medicine is ready.

0:03:23.960,0:03:26.560
The recent tonics taste very sour.

0:03:26.560,0:03:29.440
Mr Wen might have added new ingredients into it.

0:03:35.980,0:03:40.040
It hasn't been long since I got up,
but I feel sleepy again.

0:03:40.040,0:03:43.740
You've been sleeping a lot lately.

0:03:45.160,0:03:47.500
Help me get ready for a nap.

0:03:52.700,0:03:54.160
Jade,

0:03:54.160,0:03:57.440
when did I begin to sleep excessively?

0:03:57.600,0:04:03.640
About five days ago.
You sleep for almost half of the day lately.

0:04:03.640,0:04:06.640
It was around 9 am when His Majesty came here last time,

0:04:06.800,0:04:10.180
but you were still asleep ...

0:04:10.180,0:04:12.500
You also think there's something amiss, don't you?

0:04:12.600,0:04:15.460
Let me send for Mr Wen before you nap.

0:04:18.200,0:04:21.440
Go discreetly.
Say it's just a routine check.

0:04:41.280,0:04:44.940
Pardon me, My Lady.
This is going to sting slightly.

0:04:49.520,0:04:51.620
This is the Hegu acupuncture point.

0:04:51.620,0:04:56.500
The needle will indicate unusual sleepiness.

0:04:56.500,0:04:59.980
It changes color under the effect of certain drugs.

0:05:05.660,0:05:08.140
As we expected, the tonics were tampered with.

0:05:10.620,0:05:15.000
My Lady, the tip of the needle turned into light green.

0:05:15.020,0:05:17.900
What is that? Poison?

0:05:17.900,0:05:19.580
It's not that.

0:05:19.580,0:05:23.080
Someone increased the dosage
of one ingredient in the prescribed tonics.

0:05:23.080,0:05:26.560
They have been very discreet about the dosage.

0:05:26.560,0:05:30.260
It is too subtle to come to my attention between routine visits.

0:05:30.260,0:05:34.800
But if you take the medicine for a long period of time,

0:05:34.800,0:05:38.700
you will experience excessive somnolence at first

0:05:38.700,0:05:42.880
and psychotic delirium in under six months.

0:05:46.380,0:05:52.020
What a brilliant move!
They surely hold me in high regard.

0:05:52.020,0:05:57.160
It's fortunate that we discovered it.
I will prescribe treatments for you, My Lady.

0:05:58.400,0:06:04.500
This is a sinister trick. Clearly this person
attempts to subject you to death, My Lady.

0:06:07.080,0:06:12.380
Rivalries in the harem are always taken to extremes.
We can never be too effective in the defense.

0:06:13.320,0:06:18.440
Mr Wen, I would die a mysterious death without your help.

0:06:18.500,0:06:23.840
It was my negligence that caused you suffering, My Lady.

0:06:23.840,0:06:26.040
I will be particularly careful in the future.

0:06:26.040,0:06:32.000
I will prepare and serve the tonics in person
to prevent any form of meddling.

0:06:38.100,0:06:45.480
It's important to take precautions,
but the priority should be identifying the poisoner.

0:06:49.200,0:06:52.720
The tonics were prepared in my palace according to your prescriptions.

0:06:52.900,0:06:57.660
It must be my servants.

0:06:58.440,0:07:02.900
There were new servants sent to your palace last month.

0:07:03.000,0:07:09.020
The tonics were contaminated after that.

0:07:09.020,0:07:14.380
In that case, we will have to pay attention to the new servants.

0:07:14.400,0:07:17.520
What is your plan, My Lady?

0:07:17.520,0:07:22.040
I hope Mr Wen would like to put on a show with me.

0:07:22.040,0:07:26.320
We will act as if nothing happened,
not to beat the grass and alert the snakes.

0:07:26.400,0:07:29.660
Yes, My Lady.

0:07:33.600,0:07:35.520
(raising her voice) Thank you, Mr Wen.

0:07:35.520,0:07:38.980
I'm pleased to hear that I'm all right.

0:07:39.000,0:07:42.820
It is usual to feel fatigued in the spring.

0:07:42.820,0:07:45.820
You might as well take the opportunity to get more rest.

0:07:46.000,0:07:48.180
Thank you, sir.

0:07:52.980,0:07:56.160
My Lady, I found a movable brick on the courtyard wall.

0:07:56.160,0:07:58.460
It wasn't there until recently.

0:07:59.940,0:08:04.580
"Trouble resides behind one's own screen walls."

0:08:05.000,0:08:07.280
Keep it to yourself.

0:08:07.280,0:08:10.980
Watch the courtyard with Xiao-Yunzi
when they brew the medicine tomorrow.

0:08:10.980,0:08:14.100
They'll be caught red-handed.

0:08:14.100,0:08:17.000
Yes, My Lay.
Xiao-Yunzi knows kungfu.

0:08:17.000,0:08:19.740
He won't let the turncoats get away.

0:08:22.840,0:08:26.700
I bow in respect before Your Majesty.
I bow in respect before Your Highnesses.

0:08:26.800,0:08:31.080
Rise.
Have a seat.

0:08:31.080,0:08:32.980
I thank Your Majesty.

0:08:37.500,0:08:41.160
I can finally put my mind at ease
seeing Lady Shen in good health.

0:08:41.160,0:08:44.520
Lady Shen's accidental fall
turned out to be a blessing in disguise.

0:08:45.340,0:08:48.740
It regained her visitations from His Majesty,

0:08:48.740,0:08:52.140
which some of us could only wish for.

0:08:52.140,0:08:53.240
Indeed.

0:08:53.240,0:08:58.020
I was wondering why people were
swarming to the Thousand Carp Pond.

0:08:58.020,0:09:00.540
But I got my head around it afterwards.

0:09:00.540,0:09:06.100
They must have been expecting a plop
to fall into His Majesty's arms.

0:09:06.100,0:09:10.700
That is funny, Concubine Beauté.
Who would imperil their own life?

0:09:10.700,0:09:12.540
Of course,

0:09:12.540,0:09:14.820
Lady Shen has been highly favored,

0:09:14.820,0:09:20.660
unlike the old women who
turn over every stone to attract His Majesty.

0:09:21.340,0:09:25.100
Your Highness's words scared me.

0:09:25.100,0:09:28.440
We will all live to the day when we are old.

0:09:28.440,0:09:37.820
I will pray to the Buddha in the Baohua Hall
for eternal youthfulness like Your highness.

0:09:37.820,0:09:41.500
The Buddha has too many prayers to answer.

0:09:41.500,0:09:45.380
What we do matters more than what we pray.

0:09:46.460,0:09:52.160
I heard that Lady Sourire was always
by your side when you were unwell.

0:09:52.160,0:09:54.380
I wonder where she is today.

0:09:54.380,0:09:58.420
Lady Sourire abandoned her sister

0:09:58.420,0:10:01.260
when invited by His Majesty's to his study.

0:10:01.260,0:10:03.700
That's why she's absent today.

0:10:03.700,0:10:05.320
I see.

0:10:05.320,0:10:09.560
Such is the sisterhood in the palace.

0:10:14.000,0:10:16.000
We were on watch when they brew the tonic.

0:10:16.000,0:10:18.900
Violet was watching the stove and no one else was around.

0:10:32.000,0:10:34.000
It's contaminated.

0:10:38.600,0:10:41.800
I beg your pardon for our negligence, My Lady.

0:10:41.960,0:10:43.640
It's not entirely your fault.

0:10:43.640,0:10:48.040
The tonic was poisoned right under your nose

0:10:48.040,0:10:51.420
without anyone else accessing the pot.

0:10:51.420,0:10:55.340
There must be something amiss.

0:10:55.340,0:11:00.000
Jade, discard the tonic secretly.

0:11:03.140,0:11:05.040
What are you looking at?

0:11:05.700,0:11:09.660
I was thinking, if the poison wasn't
added during the brewing process,

0:11:09.660,0:11:13.160
there must be something wrong with the utensils.

0:11:13.160,0:11:16.300
Let me have a look.

0:11:21.800,0:11:24.540
I don't see anything wrong with it.

0:11:24.700,0:11:27.480
Are we thinking of it the wrong way?

0:11:39.100,0:11:41.100
Look,

0:11:41.300,0:11:46.300
the color of the lid seems to be darker than the pot.

0:11:49.080,0:11:52.400
Aiyo, it is.

0:11:52.400,0:11:55.260
You can spot the difference if you look closely.

0:11:55.260,0:11:57.820
Why is that?

0:11:59.900,0:12:04.360
Is it because the lid was simmered in the poison

0:12:04.360,0:12:08.920
to have absorbed the color of the poison?

0:12:09.760,0:12:13.800
The tonic comes into contact with the lid when it boils.

0:12:13.900,0:12:20.100
That is how the poison made its way into the tonic.

0:12:21.000,0:12:23.700
(snort) What sophistication!

0:12:23.700,0:12:26.620
No wonder our efforts were to no avail.

0:12:26.620,0:12:30.420
They have been "keeping a lid" on it.

0:12:31.600,0:12:35.020
Who is taking care of the utensils?

0:12:35.020,0:12:40.020
It used to be me, but I
gave them to Spica, the newcomer.

0:12:41.700,0:12:43.200
- Xiao-Yunzi.
- Yes.

0:12:43.300,0:12:46.860
Discard the tonic and put the pot back.
Do it discreetly.

0:12:49.060,0:12:52.000
And inquire about Spicas's background for me.

0:13:01.260,0:13:03.400
Mr Yun.

0:13:04.360,0:13:08.160
Spica, why did you sneak behind my back?

0:13:09.200,0:13:13.580
Mr Yun, what brings you to the kitchen?
I hope you can pardon the sootiness.

0:13:13.580,0:13:17.380
I am the head eunuch of the palace.
I go anywhere I want.

0:13:17.380,0:13:22.640
Why are you still using that shabby pot to brew tonics for My Lady?

0:13:22.640,0:13:25.140
It looks as if My Lady had fallen from grace.

0:13:25.140,0:13:26.920
Get a new one immediately.

0:13:26.920,0:13:32.500
Sir, you might not know that an older pot brews better tonics.

0:13:32.620,0:13:35.700
A new pot reduces the potency of the medicine.

0:13:35.700,0:13:38.200
You know better, don't you?

0:13:38.200,0:13:40.440
We'll keep the pot for now.

0:13:41.440,0:13:44.060
Keep up the good work.

0:13:44.820,0:13:48.220
Oh, My Lady is napping after the morning tonic.

0:13:48.220,0:13:50.660
You should prepare the evening tonic soon.

0:13:58.340,0:14:01.700
My Lady, Spica used to work for Escort Yu.

0:14:01.700,0:14:07.900
She was one of the maids
that were sent away upon Yu's demotion.

0:14:08.500,0:14:11.700
Interesting.
An avenger for Yu.

0:14:12.500,0:14:15.860
What a loyal maid to her former mistress.

0:14:15.860,0:14:18.000
Bring her here to see me.

0:14:18.000,0:14:19.000
Yes.

0:14:19.000,0:14:23.300
Ah, get some of burning charcoals from the kitchen.

0:14:23.360,0:14:25.040
They will be come in handy.

0:14:32.700,0:14:36.220
Good to see you here, Jade.
The evening tonic is almost ready.

0:14:36.220,0:14:39.140
It's okay, I will stay here for a bit.

0:14:39.200,0:14:42.640
Mr Wen selected the best medicine for My Lady.

0:14:42.640,0:14:45.660
I've been watching it carefully.

0:14:46.580,0:14:51.520
Spica, you are very loyal to My Lady as a newcomer.

0:14:51.600,0:14:54.680
It is an honor to serve Lady Sourire.

0:14:54.680,0:14:56.100
I must do my best.

0:14:56.100,0:14:59.080
My Lady appreciates your hard work.
She wishes to reward you.

0:14:59.100,0:15:01.100
You should go quickly.

0:15:01.100,0:15:02.940
My Lady wishes to reward me?

0:15:02.940,0:15:06.020
Go quickly.
My Lady is waiting.

0:15:06.020,0:15:08.800
Bring the stove to keep the tonic warm.

0:15:11.600,0:15:15.460
Raise your head.
We won't eat you.

0:15:19.640,0:15:23.760
Don't be scared.
I simply wish to talk to you.

0:15:26.100,0:15:31.020
Jinxi told me that you have been a competent maid.

0:15:31.760,0:15:35.800
I appreciate that.
I wonder what I should reward you

0:15:35.800,0:15:39.820
so that the other servants will follow your example.

0:15:39.820,0:15:42.880
Thank you, My Lady.
I simply did my job.

0:15:42.880,0:15:46.100
You stand out from the newcomers to my palace.

0:15:47.500,0:15:52.740
I wonder which concubine you used to work for.
Why would she send you away?

0:15:54.460,0:15:58.080
I was too humble to work for any notable concubine.

0:15:58.080,0:16:02.980
I am honored to be your maid.
It must be the good karma from my past lives.

0:16:04.100,0:16:08.980
Escort Yu is not a notable concubine
due to her demotion.

0:16:08.980,0:16:12.160
But what did she offer you

0:16:12.160,0:16:16.220
to make you commit the heinous crime?

0:16:16.980,0:16:19.340
I did serve Escort Yu,

0:16:19.340,0:16:22.440
but I have no idea what you're talking about, My Lady.

0:16:22.440,0:16:24.040
You don't know what I'm talking about?

0:16:24.960,0:16:28.000
What happened to the lid of my brew pot?

0:16:28.640,0:16:30.140
I have no idea!

0:16:30.140,0:16:33.740
I am loyal to you, My Lady!

0:16:36.240,0:16:42.180
If you say so, we will give you
a chance to prove your loyalty.

0:16:42.180,0:16:46.120
My Lady has to be cautious
for you have worked for Escort Yu.

0:16:46.120,0:16:50.400
You can prove your innocence and loyalty
by holding a charcoal in your hand.

0:16:50.400,0:16:52.100
And we all will treat you nicely.

0:16:54.780,0:16:56.840
Do it!

0:17:03.780,0:17:05.560
You are scared, aren't you?

0:17:05.560,0:17:08.980
How fake your loyalty is!

0:17:20.020,0:17:23.540
Please spare me, My Lady.
Please spare me!

0:17:24.100,0:17:29.800
Tell me the truth,
or you will be flogged to death.

0:17:30.760,0:17:35.840
One day, after I was sent to the Palace of Pearl Jade,
Escort Yu asked me to see her.

0:17:35.840,0:17:40.800
She gave me a lot of money
and forced me to do this for her.

0:17:40.820,0:17:44.240
I'm such a fool, My Lady!

0:17:44.500,0:17:47.960
I beg your forgiveness, My Lady!

0:17:47.960,0:17:52.200
Go on, this is your chance to atone for your crime.

0:17:52.360,0:17:54.980
But I won't tolerate a word of dishonesty.

0:17:56.120,0:18:03.780
Escort Yu said all I needed to do
was to put poison in your tonics and food.

0:18:04.500,0:18:08.560
I made a moving brick on the wall
at Yu's command.

0:18:08.560,0:18:16.800
She had messages and objects
passed to me through the hole.

0:18:16.800,0:18:19.240
That is how the poison was passed in?

0:18:19.860,0:18:23.700
And she taught you to simmer the lid with the poison?

0:18:24.700,0:18:26.160
Do you have any accomplices?

0:18:26.160,0:18:29.200
No, there's no one else!

0:18:29.920,0:18:34.600
When does Yu send in messages and the poison?

0:18:35.260,0:18:36.520
Hmm ...

0:18:37.440,0:18:40.160
Xiao-Yunzi, put the charcoal in her mouth!

0:18:40.160,0:18:42.440
I'll say! I'll say!

0:18:43.020,0:18:50.060
She sends in the poison every other day.
I'll go to pick it up.

0:18:50.060,0:18:53.740
Every other day?
So tonight?

0:18:55.040,0:18:57.560
What time is the pick-up?
Is there any code word?

0:18:57.560,0:19:03.320
At 7 pm, there goes cuckoo on the other side of the wall.

0:19:03.320,0:19:06.280
I will make a cuckoo sound in response.

0:19:06.280,0:19:08.040
Did you see who that was?

0:19:08.040,0:19:11.000
No, I couldn't see.

0:19:11.160,0:19:15.820
But I know it's a man from his hand.
There's a scar in the palm of his right hand.

0:19:19.620,0:19:25.280
Xiao-Yunzi, tie her up in the storeroom.
Keep her alive.

0:19:25.880,0:19:30.060
Say she's sent to Lady Shen if anyone asks.

0:19:31.380,0:19:33.320
Go!

0:19:37.400,0:19:41.900
Jinxi, you will pick up the poison in place of Spica.

0:19:42.000,0:19:46.300
Select a few eunuchs to assist Xiao-Yunzi.

0:19:46.300,0:19:49.000
Yes, I'll go get ready.

0:19:51.800,0:19:55.860
I need to tell Meizhuang about this.

0:19:55.860,0:20:00.400
Yes, it's a good idea to plan with Lady Shen.

0:20:02.240,0:20:03.760
What about Companion An?

0:20:03.760,0:20:07.960
Let's not give trouble to her faint heart.

0:20:08.000,0:20:09.940
Certainly.

0:20:09.940,0:20:15.120
You must make up your mind, My Lady.
Don't compromise yourself this time!

0:20:20.000,0:20:23.580
My Lady, Xiao-Yunzi is up on the roof.

0:20:26.500,0:20:29.800
He'll jump and catch the culprit.

0:20:32.020,0:20:34.040
I'll be standing by the wall.

0:20:35.260,0:20:41.500
It's good that Xiao-Yunzi knows kungfu.
He's well disguised by the darkness.

