0:21:15.460,0:21:17.440
Got him!
Xiao-Yunzi, we got him!

0:21:17.440,0:21:19.160
Go, go quickly!

0:21:19.160,0:21:21.100
Go get him!

0:21:25.000,0:21:26.020
Go!

0:21:26.020,0:21:28.160
- Let me go! I'm begging of you!
- Be quiet!

0:21:30.000,0:21:32.000
- Let me go!
- Be quiet!

0:21:33.200,0:21:35.100
- Please let me go!
- On your knees!

0:21:35.100,0:21:36.580
My Lady, please let me go!

0:21:36.580,0:21:39.280
Hold up his head.
I'm afraid it's an old friend.

0:21:41.200,0:21:42.760
Xiao-Yinzi?

0:21:43.480,0:21:45.800
Mr Yin, I trust you've been well.

0:21:46.000,0:21:47.580
Peace to Lady Sourire.

0:21:48.000,0:21:51.800
We used to be mistress and servant.

0:21:51.800,0:21:53.920
You will just need to answer my questions.

0:21:56.180,0:21:57.540
Are the sticks in place?

0:21:57.540,0:21:59.660
Yes, My Lady.

0:22:00.320,0:22:02.800
Who do you work for currently?

0:22:04.000,0:22:05.880
For Escort Yu.

0:22:05.880,0:22:07.600
That must be a waste of your talent.

0:22:07.600,0:22:11.520
I don't feel that way.
A servant doesn't get to pick his mistress.

0:22:12.680,0:22:15.160
It's good that you can look on the bright side of life.

0:22:15.160,0:22:18.700
Didn't you follow your shifu to work for Concubine Beauté?

0:22:18.700,0:22:20.780
Why were you sent to Escort Yu?

0:22:20.780,0:22:24.140
Shifu offended Concubine Beauté
for his intention to work for you.

0:22:24.140,0:22:26.580
Concubine Beauté began to disdain me as well.

0:22:26.580,0:22:30.700
Her Highness sent me to serve Escort Yu
as a chance to redeem myself.

0:22:31.000,0:22:33.500
She thinks long-term for you, doesn't she?

0:22:35.720,0:22:40.600
Now tell me, what were you doing
outside my palace at this time?

0:22:41.580,0:22:43.220
I ...

0:22:44.760,0:22:46.400
- Xiao-Yunzi.
- Yes.

0:22:46.400,0:22:49.460
Slap this ungrateful turncoat

0:22:50.140,0:22:52.140
until he speaks the truth.

0:22:53.180,0:22:55.380
Please spare me, My Lady!

0:22:56.180,0:22:58.160
My Lady ...

0:22:58.160,0:23:01.000
please spare me ... My Lady!

0:23:02.100,0:23:04.200
I am telling the truth!

0:23:04.200,0:23:05.600
Please spare me!

0:23:11.860,0:23:15.620
My Lady, that weasel confessed everything under torture.

0:23:15.620,0:23:17.500
He said that Escort Yu instructed him to come here.

0:23:17.500,0:23:21.140
Tie him up in the storeroom as well.
Keep watch on him and Spica.

0:23:24.440,0:23:27.440
I feel bitterly, bitterly disappointed.

0:23:27.440,0:23:29.720
I treated him so nicely.

0:23:29.720,0:23:32.200
Don't feel disappointed by that trash.

0:23:32.200,0:23:37.380
Now it is clear that Yu took revenge grudgingly.

0:23:37.500,0:23:42.200
I have been extremely tolerant of Yu.
But when I give her an inch, she takes an ell.

0:23:43.120,0:23:47.460
Meizhuang, why is it so difficult
to have some peace in the palace?

0:23:47.460,0:23:51.460
"One has no intention of harm
while the tiger does."

0:23:51.960,0:23:55.180
You and I, we never meant to harm anyone.

0:23:55.180,0:23:58.940
But they want to take our lives.

0:23:59.000,0:24:02.840
I have to report this to His Majesty and the Empress.

0:24:02.840,0:24:05.480
There's no refuting of the concrete evidence against Yu.

0:24:05.500,0:24:10.920
But I'm afraid His Majesty would still have feelings for her.

0:24:11.940,0:24:17.300
She might be excused from death
for her futile attempt to poison and curse My Lady.

0:24:18.000,0:24:21.880
But deception of His Majesty is a capital offence.

0:24:22.520,0:24:29.780
My Lady, do you remember that I asked you whether
"fish eyes were passed off as pearls" on New Year's Eve?

0:24:36.700,0:24:38.200
Your Highness ...

0:24:38.200,0:24:39.500
What is so urgent?

0:24:39.500,0:24:41.800
Xiao-Yinzi didn't return to Yu last night.

0:24:41.800,0:24:44.820
I was just informed that
he has been kept in the Palace of Pearl Jade.

0:24:45.760,0:24:47.160
Useless eunuch!

0:24:47.160,0:24:51.840
Your Highness, that castrated pig must have
confessed everything under torture.

0:24:51.840,0:24:55.980
Escort Yu will be held responsible.
What if she rat us out?

0:24:55.980,0:24:57.600
What do you suggest?

0:24:57.600,0:24:59.240
Finish one to finish all.

0:24:59.240,0:25:00.500
No,

0:25:00.500,0:25:03.540
it will be suspicious to make a move right now.

0:25:03.540,0:25:07.040
She has to take this to her grave.

0:25:08.000,0:25:14.200
She wanted to kill Zhen Huan for herself.
Why would she choose to help us over a chance to survive?

0:25:14.200,0:25:18.660
She would choose her family's survival over her own.

0:25:27.000,0:25:29.040
Why did you take so long?

0:25:29.040,0:25:32.000
I had to try to make it clear.
I'm not an articulate maid.

0:25:32.500,0:25:35.360
Says your silver tongue.

0:25:35.360,0:25:39.760
You not only need to make it clear,
but also appeal to His Majesty emotionally.

0:25:40.500,0:25:42.320
Thank you for your advice, sir.

0:25:42.820,0:25:45.940
Aiyo, don't do that to an old friend!

0:25:46.600,0:25:48.620
What did His Majesty say?

0:25:48.620,0:25:53.380
You'll listen for yourself.
I'll be much obliged for your help.

0:25:54.000,0:25:55.560
Su Peisheng!

0:26:01.000,0:26:03.000
Who are you?
How dare you break into my palace?

0:26:03.000,0:26:05.720
Yu is banished to the Cold Palace
by His Majesty's decree.

0:26:07.460,0:26:10.400
I don't believe this!
I don't believe this!

0:26:10.400,0:26:13.640
I need to see His Majesty!
I need to see His Majesty!

0:26:13.640,0:26:15.560
His Majesty has no intention to see you!

0:26:15.560,0:26:16.220
Go!

0:26:16.220,0:26:18.180
I don't believe this!
I need to see His Majesty!

0:26:27.700,0:26:30.980
Peace and grace to Your Majesty.

0:26:30.980,0:26:33.780
- Rise.
- I thank Your Majesty.

0:26:34.660,0:26:36.600
Did you sleep well last night?

0:26:36.600,0:26:38.420
I thank Your Majesty.

0:26:38.420,0:26:41.360
It was dangerous to sleep too well.

0:26:41.360,0:26:42.800
I understand.

0:26:42.800,0:26:46.420
Jinxi has reported to me and the Empress.

0:26:47.000,0:26:51.600
I will have your tonics and food
closely monitored in the future.

0:26:51.600,0:26:54.600
This will never happen again.

0:26:54.600,0:26:58.340
It was also my fault to be oblivious.

0:26:58.340,0:27:06.740
It wasn't your fault.
It was the bitter rivalry beyond imagination.

0:27:06.740,0:27:10.320
Spica and Xiao-Yinzi were flogged to death.

0:27:10.320,0:27:15.680
And Yu will be confined to the Cold Palace
for the rest of her life.

0:27:15.680,0:27:19.360
Huan Huan, you are out of harm's way.

0:27:19.500,0:27:22.380
I never meant to vie with anyone.

0:27:22.380,0:27:27.840
So many people died
for my unintentional offence to Yu.

0:27:27.840,0:27:32.140
I am a sinful concubine,
unworthy of Your Majesty's favor.

0:27:32.140,0:27:34.640
Don't overthink.

0:27:34.640,0:27:40.400
You've been the innocent victim to a series of appalling events.
Take it easy on yourself.

0:27:41.140,0:27:44.100
I made a wish on New Year's Eve

0:27:44.100,0:27:49.360
that the northern wind could spare the blooming plums.

0:27:50.180,0:27:52.680
But that ended up unfulfilled.

0:27:54.080,0:27:58.720
Where did you make the wish?
And what did you say for your wish?

0:27:59.000,0:28:02.560
In the Garden of Leaning Plums.

0:28:02.600,0:28:07.960
I wished “If the northern wind can hear the plum flowers, 
spare the blooming wishes for a peaceful spring."

0:28:08.680,0:28:13.960
I remember wetting my shoes in the snow that night.

0:28:13.960,0:28:16.700
Did you run into anyone?

0:28:16.860,0:28:18.780
Si Lang, how did you know?

0:28:19.000,0:28:25.460
That night, in the garden,
I ran into a male stranger.

0:28:26.520,0:28:30.200
As I was out without permission
and had to avoid contact with a male stranger,

0:28:30.200,0:28:33.720
I got away saying that I was a maid working in the garden.

0:28:37.500,0:28:40.580
Was the stranger that night ...

0:28:41.360,0:28:44.940
I apologize for my ill manners.
I didn't know it was Your Majesty.

0:28:45.900,0:28:51.180
It was you?
So it was you!

0:28:51.820,0:28:54.840
I mistook her.

0:28:55.000,0:28:56.460
Su Peisheng!

0:28:56.460,0:28:57.880
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:28:57.880,0:29:01.000
Make the announcement that
Yu in the Cold Palace is granted options for suicide

0:29:01.000,0:29:03.740
for deceiving me and poisoning a concubine.

0:29:03.740,0:29:06.080
Yes, I'll do it immediately.

0:29:07.460,0:29:11.080
What was wrong?
Why would Your Majesty grant her suicide?

0:29:11.080,0:29:17.980
She lied to me, saying that
she was the person who spoke to me that night.

0:29:18.000,0:29:20.900
She became a concubine because of that,

0:29:20.900,0:29:25.700
and caused offence to her superiors time and again.

0:29:25.720,0:29:28.540
Now her crimes are unpardonable.

0:29:28.600,0:29:32.780
She made mistakes because she admired Your Majesty.

0:29:32.780,0:29:37.640
An emperor's words count.
She is unpardonable.

0:29:37.700,0:29:43.700
But if you plead her case,
I will allow her corpse to be sent home.

0:29:44.700,0:29:46.500
I thank Your Majesty.

0:30:00.100,0:30:05.080
Did you bring any luck charm with you
to the garden that night?

0:30:06.000,0:30:10.680
like a sachet, a fan pendant, or a hairpin?

0:30:11.420,0:30:13.980
Just a trinket I liked.

0:30:13.980,0:30:17.720
I can make another one for Si Lang if you like.

0:30:18.720,0:30:25.500
You've been unnerved lately.
Worry about that when you get over it.

0:30:26.500,0:30:30.760
I'm in no hurry to spend decades with you.

0:30:31.480,0:30:34.380
There was one more thing I summoned you for.

0:30:34.380,0:30:37.380
The Ministry of Revenue proposed
a new farmland planning measure.

0:30:37.380,0:30:42.080
Opinions vary about the proposal.

0:30:42.080,0:30:48.320
I'd rather go investigate by myself
than listen to the endless debates.

0:30:48.500,0:30:52.100
I'll go to the suburbs.
The trip will take a few days.

0:30:52.260,0:30:56.480
Farming is a matter of life and death for the people.

0:30:57.420,0:30:59.240
When will Your Majesty leave?

0:30:59.240,0:31:02.660
I can leave right away.

0:31:03.380,0:31:07.720
Please take the best care of yourself
during the trip.

0:31:09.060,0:31:14.220
I wanted to go with Su Peisheng,
but it's not so convenient for a eunuch.

0:31:14.220,0:31:20.020
But don't worry, I traveled a lot for
the prior emperor as the State Prince.

0:31:21.040,0:31:25.440
Take care of yourself.
I'll be back in no time.

0:31:27.480,0:31:29.900
How is Lady Cao's job going?

0:31:29.900,0:31:33.160
She's been a quiet person,

0:31:33.160,0:31:36.580
but she talks sense whenever she speaks.

0:31:36.900,0:31:39.740
She's been taking care of Yu's family.

0:31:40.480,0:31:42.300
That is very thoughtful of her.

0:31:42.300,0:31:47.960
What use will she be
if she can't even sort things out for Your Highness?

0:31:48.000,0:31:52.880
But you used to be a
more favored concubine of His Majesty.

0:31:52.880,0:31:55.320
Why's that different now?

0:31:56.220,0:32:00.060
Because she has a daughter.

0:32:00.060,0:32:02.600
That gets her to see His Majesty oftener.

0:32:02.600,0:32:07.260
True, even if it is a daughter.

0:32:11.680,0:32:14.780
Why is everyone so quiet today?

0:32:18.820,0:32:21.000
I feel suffocated.

0:32:21.000,0:32:22.840
What's wrong?

0:32:22.840,0:32:27.760
I hate being ambushed,
and I was resentful of Spica and Xiao-Yinzi.

0:32:27.760,0:32:33.340
But when His Majesty executed them,
it didn't ease my mind.

0:32:33.340,0:32:38.080
Me neither.
No ones would take heart from the death of another.

0:32:38.080,0:32:41.840
There is yet one after another to be defeated.

0:32:41.840,0:32:43.760
Then we'll deal with one after another.

0:32:43.760,0:32:47.060
They will be defeated as long as
we are of one heart and one mind.

0:32:48.000,0:32:52.020
But Sourire, why would you keep this from me?

0:32:52.020,0:32:59.300
It was not until this morning that
I heard about it from the Empress.

0:32:59.380,0:33:01.440
I didn't meant to hide anything from you.

0:33:01.440,0:33:05.860
It's better to hear nothing of such a frightful incident.

0:33:05.860,0:33:11.820
But I see you as my own sister.
Sisters would share cares and burdens.

0:33:11.820,0:33:14.160
It's fortunate that this is over.

0:33:15.100,0:33:17.060
I'm grateful that you are all right.

0:33:17.060,0:33:24.120
His Majesty has granted suicide to Yu.
That is the fate for any intender of harm.

0:33:25.980,0:33:30.240
Soft-spoken as she is,
Lingrong has a strong mind.

0:33:30.240,0:33:31.580
My Lady!

0:33:34.420,0:33:37.920
Yu refuses to commit suicide.
She kicked up a tremendous row in the Cold Palace

0:33:37.920,0:33:40.760
yelling that she has to see His Majesty before she dies.

0:33:40.760,0:33:42.000
How?

0:33:42.000,0:33:44.940
His Majesty must have left the palace by now.

0:33:44.940,0:33:47.680
It's impossible to keep her alive
until His Majesty comes back.

0:33:47.680,0:33:49.140
Is it reported to the Empress?

0:33:49.140,0:33:54.280
Her Majesty has been bed-ridden with cephalalgia lately.
We can't count on her.

0:33:55.500,0:33:57.780
In that case, there's only
Consort Fleur that we can count on ...

0:33:57.780,0:34:02.420
Her Highness said that she's been indisposed.

0:34:02.420,0:34:07.240
She was close with Yu.
Now she wouldn't have the least connection with her.

0:34:08.420,0:34:13.140
Yu insists that she's been slandered.
She insanely smashed the poison granted to her.

0:34:13.140,0:34:17.300
She even curses My Lady
blatantly and viciously in the Cold Palace.

0:34:17.500,0:34:21.320
Let her be.
Last-ditch protest.

0:34:22.180,0:34:27.080
Sourire, I think it's time that I should go.

0:34:28.360,0:34:31.620
- Take care.
- Goodbye, Lingrong.

0:34:39.000,0:34:42.900
Cuckoo, what is the Cold Palace?

0:34:42.900,0:34:45.840
It the palace for the banished concubines.

0:34:45.840,0:34:53.300
Many of them ended up dead or psychotic
during their confinement.

0:34:53.300,0:34:57.460
It is considered a haunted place.

0:34:57.460,0:34:59.000
So no one visits the Cold Palace?

0:34:59.000,0:35:01.000
What the hell of a place is that?

0:35:01.000,0:35:06.180
Servants near the Cold Palace repeatedly saw
ghosts that kept crying night after night.

0:35:06.180,0:35:08.180
It's horrifying.

0:35:10.560,0:35:12.600
I will go for a check.

0:35:19.460,0:35:23.000
My Lady, let's not go inside.
It gives me the creeps.

0:35:24.360,0:35:26.900
(Let me go! Let go!)

0:35:26.900,0:35:30.320
Let me go! Let go of me!

0:35:30.320,0:35:34.020
Yu, accept your fate.

0:35:34.020,0:35:36.500
Let me go!

0:35:37.840,0:35:39.740
Let go!

0:35:42.800,0:35:45.180
Why did you come here, Companion An?

0:35:45.180,0:35:49.360
Sourire heard that Yu has been cursing her.
She sent me here to look into it.

0:35:50.400,0:35:53.380
Le me go! Let go!

0:35:53.380,0:35:57.520
It seems that you haven't finished the job, sir?

0:35:58.220,0:36:00.280
She's untamed.

0:36:00.280,0:36:03.040
Why are you here?
Why are you here!

0:36:03.500,0:36:04.780
Where is His Majesty?

0:36:04.780,0:36:07.000
Let me go!

0:36:07.920,0:36:09.480
Pull her away!

0:36:09.480,0:36:12.300
Why would His Majesty
set his noble foot on the Cold Palace?

0:36:13.240,0:36:17.200
It was all because of Zhen Huan!
It was all that bitch!

0:36:18.580,0:36:22.820
She wooed His Majesty into killing me!

0:36:22.820,0:36:27.140
I suppose you wish to know
why you are granted suicide, don't you?

0:36:28.280,0:36:30.440
I'll do the favor to tell you.

0:36:30.440,0:36:33.980
It was you that had Sourire's tonics poinsoned, wasn't it?

0:36:36.440,0:36:40.880
Yes, I arranged that.

0:36:41.500,0:36:50.000
But it was her who made me fall from grace
to this humble existence!

0:36:50.100,0:36:54.680
I wish to drink her blood and chew her bones.

0:36:54.680,0:36:57.500
I wish that bitch will live in hell life after life.

0:36:57.500,0:36:59.400
You wish?

0:36:59.400,0:37:02.640
You don't even get to have a wish
when winner takes all.

0:37:04.020,0:37:06.800
No, I must not die.

0:37:06.800,0:37:12.900
I encountered His Majesty on New Year's Eve.

0:37:13.720,0:37:17.640
His Majesty likes to hear me sing Kunqu Opera.

0:37:17.640,0:37:20.440
He wouldn't let me die.

0:37:20.440,0:37:26.620
“If the northern wind can hear the plum flowers,
spare the blooming wishes for a peaceful spring."

0:37:26.620,0:37:31.800
You pretended to be Sourire on New Year's Eve.
Have you no shame?

0:37:35.500,0:37:41.280
It was her ... It was her!

0:37:42.240,0:37:46.940
No, I must not die.
I must not die!

0:37:47.000,0:37:52.380
Your Majesty ... Your Majesty ...

0:37:52.380,0:37:54.300
You like my Kunqu Opera.

0:37:54.300,0:37:56.300
May I have a word with you, sir?

0:37:56.300,0:38:01.240
I will sing Kunqu for Your Majesty!

0:38:02.100,0:38:04.000
My Lady.
(Your Majesty ...)

0:38:04.000,0:38:07.380
His Majesty is away while the Empress
is having a seizure of cephalalgia.

0:38:07.380,0:38:09.780
This madness must be stopped.

0:38:09.780,0:38:12.000
Your Majesty ...

0:38:12.000,0:38:14.460
My Lady, Yu was granted suicide.

0:38:14.460,0:38:17.620
But this madwoman smashed
the cup of poison and tore up the silk noose.

0:38:17.620,0:38:19.440
There's nothing we can do about her.

0:38:20.300,0:38:23.140
Sir, you have served His Majesty for long, haven't you?

0:38:23.300,0:38:26.520
Yes, for over 30 years.

0:38:27.360,0:38:31.600
Sir, you are a most knowledgeable person in the palace and much appreciated for you hard work.

0:38:31.600,0:38:33.820
You understand His Majesty the best.

0:38:33.900,0:38:40.140
Now that His Majesty is away,
should we keep her alive until he returns?

0:38:40.640,0:38:42.440
Would you suggest ...

0:38:42.440,0:38:47.460
Sir, your work is done when she is dead.

0:38:48.000,0:38:51.000
No one would investigate how she dies.

0:38:51.000,0:38:58.480
For instance, what would happen if a concubine refused
to be buried alive with a deceased emperor?

0:39:00.060,0:39:01.740
My Lady, I understand.

0:39:01.740,0:39:05.320
Sir, I hope you understand
"one has more dreams the longer he sleeps".

0:39:05.320,0:39:08.460
It puts an end to His Majesty's concern
when you terminate her life.

0:39:08.460,0:39:12.440
Yes, I bid you goodbye, My Lady.

0:39:14.440,0:39:18.120
Your Majesty ...
Help me, Your Majesty!

0:39:18.120,0:39:20.220
Your Majesty ...

0:39:22.000,0:39:27.660
Zhen Huan, you will be terminated,
whether by me or not!

0:39:27.660,0:39:30.020
You will go to hell!

0:39:30.020,0:39:32.340
What impenitence at death!

0:39:32.340,0:39:37.260
Yu will die for sure, but why would you
make a trip to this spooky place, My Lady?

0:39:39.000,0:39:43.720
I want Sourire to know that
there's something I can do for her.

0:39:44.200,0:39:48.760
You end up with eunuchs,
who you never treated as humans.

0:39:50.300,0:39:52.760
- Xiao-Xiazi.
- Yes.

0:39:52.760,0:39:57.220
We had to be tolerant of her,
but not anymore.

0:40:10.180,0:40:14.660
No! No!

0:40:14.660,0:40:17.820
I am a concubine.
You cannot kill me!

0:40:17.820,0:40:19.500
You cannot kill me!

0:40:23.520,0:40:26.500
Peace to Lady Sourire.
Peace to Lady Shen.

0:40:26.700,0:40:30.080
I wish to report to you that Yu committed suicide.

0:40:32.360,0:40:34.060
